Example <pre><code>{
"latE7": 414216106,
"lngE7": 21684775
}
</code></pre> Property Description <code>latE7</code> Latitude<code>integer</code>Example: <code>414216106</code>Latitude coordinate of the waypoint. Degrees multiplied by 10^7 and rounded to the nearest integer, in the range -900000000 to +900000000 (divide value by 10^7 for the usual range -90° to +90°). <code>lngE7</code> Longitude<code>integer</code>Example: <code>21684775</code>Longitude coordinate of the waypoint. Degrees multiplied by 10^7 and rounded to the nearest integer, in the range -1800000000 to +1800000000 (divide value by 10^7 for the usual range -180° to +180°).
